overview: Kennedys Karne | Original Carne Asada, Butcher Shop, Organic Grocery For Over 50 years, Kennedys Karne has sold the finest and tastiest meats. Featuring our USDA Certified Angus Beef Brand Beef, as well as premium marinated Chicken & Pork. Beef Carne Asada,Carne Asada, “grilled meat”, is the authentic mexican style marinated beef. Kennedys Karne prides itself on the finest carne asada in the world.Chicken Pollo Asada Pollo Asada, “Grilled Chicken”, Pollo Asada is Mexican style marinated Chicken.All Natural From our home made tortillas to our natural sea salt marinades to our all natural grain fed hormone free meats. Kennedys Karne is quality you can taste. Award Winning 16 time Carne Asada world Champions. Kennedys renowned natural foods.
